              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/14243923/" class="">第七章 “中西杂拌”---阎锡山</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/combine/" class=" " title="combine">combine</a>
                (give it a fly)
              
                <span class="allstar40" title="推荐"></span>
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="14243923">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">我类个去～～～
看了这个才知道，阎锡山才是TG的学习楷模和集权统治的滥觞。</span>
